How many users are currently online on mycompanywebsite.com, and where are they from?
Begin!

Due to the limitation of toolset, I cannot solve the question. 

The APIs available to me (checkhealth_for_squake and projects_for_squake) are related to a tool called "squake", and they do not provide website visitor or user tracking information. To answer questions about website user statistics, I would need access to web analytics tools like Google Analytics, which are not present in my current toolset.
